snippet.title: Body Conscious Part 1: Shinjuku & Takashi Digital Rave! [3DO]
snippet.description:
Body Conscious Part 1: Shinjuku & Takashi Digital Rave!

Another one of those Japanese-only 'games' that truly defined the 3DO as the ultimate multimedia masterpiece of the early 90s. (In other words, it's just a video formatted to only play on the 3DO system)
